scopecontent.p: Possibly a variable star catalog?

Book is a catalogue of worldwide contemporary variable star discoveries, 1900-1926, accrued via announcements which appear in international astronomical publications (e.g., AN 154 (1900) pp. 77-79; AN 211 (1920) pp.191-192) and in Harvard College Observatory serials (e.g., Har Circ 191 (1910) pp. 1-3; Har Circ 158 (1910) pp. 1-3.)
